\c 3
\s Mukadzi wechipiri woufeve waHosiya anofananidzira Israeri
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha akati kwandiri, Chiendazve, undoda mukadzi anodikanwa nomurume wake, asi chiri chifeve, sezvinoda Jehovha vana vaIsraeri, kunyange vachitsaukira kuna vamwe vamwari, vachida mapundu amadzamb iringa.
\p
\v 2 Naizvozvo ndakamutenga namasirivha ane gumi namashanu, nehomeri yebhari, nehomeri yebhari;
\v 3 ndikati kwaari, Uchafanira kundimirira mazuva mazhinji; haufaniri kupata, haufaniri kuva mukadzi womumwe murume; neniwo ndichaita saizvozvo kwauri.
\v 4 nokuti vana vaIsraeri vachagara mazuva mazhinji vasina mambo, vasina muchinda, vasina zvibairo vasina shongwe vasina efodhi kana terafimi.
\v 5 Pashure vana vaIsraeri vachadzoka vachitsvaka Jehovha Mwari wavo naDhavhidhi mambo wavo; vachauya kuna Jehovha vachitya, nokuunyoro hwake namazuva okupedzisira.
